 <para>
  &gnome; Videos is the default movie player. &gnome; Videos provides the
  following multimedia features:
 </para>
 <itemizedlist mark="bullet" spacing="normal">
  <listitem>
   <para>
    Support for a variety of video and audio files
   </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
   <para>
    A variety of zoom levels and aspect ratios, and a full screen view
   </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
   <para>
    Seek and volume controls
   </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
   <para>
    Playlists
   </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
   <para>
    Complete keyboard navigation
   </para>
  </listitem>
